{"tid":525039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】湖南煙花廠爆炸 混火藥工人傷重亡","createTime":"2018-01-10T08:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T08:21:13.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1093695ace0a3558afadb082b994c347117b5f6b","tid":525039,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180110/large/1515569601_fbb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180110%2Flarge%2F1515569601_fbb4.jpg&h=543f6d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖南長沙寧鄉市大成橋鎮一間煙花廠，今早8時15分許發生爆炸，導致1人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n出事煙花廠為湖南銀意煙花燃放製造有限公司機械混藥房，事故中一名姓杜的混藥工人（48歲，湖南安化人）身受重傷，送院途中死亡。當局現正調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180110/57689691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F57689691&d=0F%2F3G%2BKy%2F4cf3VPMUpUJ2aNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=ec919a89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F57689691&h=ca6cfe5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180110/57689691</a>"}]}